{"id":1740,"date":"2019-09-25T04:49:20","date_gmt":"2019-09-25T04:49:20","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/99rockingtees.teesbank.website\/?page_id=1740"},"modified":"2022-06-20T03:41:35","modified_gmt":"2022-06-20T03:41:35","slug":"rodent-control","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/rodent-control\/","title":{"rendered":"Rodent Control"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1740\" class=\"elementor elementor-1740\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-12f2e2a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"12f2e2a\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-916852a\" data-id=\"916852a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c159337 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c159337\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">RODENT REMOVAL YOU CAN TRUST!<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-72a6b1d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"72a6b1d\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-4671d86\" data-id=\"4671d86\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-009bd11 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"009bd11\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"666\" src=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/shutterstock_773636719-compressor-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3476\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/shutterstock_773636719-compressor-1.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/shutterstock_773636719-compressor-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/shutterstock_773636719-compressor-1-768x511.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-008afa5\" data-id=\"008afa5\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-35cb9ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"35cb9ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Your property may become a\u00a0<a title=\"home\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/\">home<\/a>\u00a0to rats and mice that can make a whole mess out of your house. Even an impeccable sanitation is not a guarantee for a rodent-free life. Large houses give mice more entries and opportunities to grow population inside your home, regardless of how much effort you put into keeping your house clean. If food is easily available to rodents, they will spread around the house easily and rapidly. The only way to stop this is an effective rodent control that ACME offers in Mississauga, Oakville, Brampton and Milton for the most convenient prices.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a94d6d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a94d6d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ONE OF THE REASONS WHY MICE CONTROL IS SO IMPORTANT IS: <\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2dbb08d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2dbb08d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>The number of diseases that rodents can spread. Some of the most common diseases passed by mice and mouse droppings are:\u00a0<\/div><ul><li>Hantavirus<\/li><li class=\"aio-icon-title ult-responsive\" data-ultimate-target=\"#Info-box-wrap-3274 .aio-icon-title\" data-responsive-json-new=\"{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">Bubonic Plague<\/li><li class=\"aio-icon-title ult-responsive\" data-ultimate-target=\"#Info-box-wrap-8741 .aio-icon-title\" data-responsive-json-new=\"{&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;line-height&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">Rat-Bite Fever<\/li><li>Salmonellosis (also known as Salmonella)<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a8d136 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7a8d136\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>All the listed diseases leave serious consequences to humans and can even be fatal. A mice exterminator can detect mice in your house before they invade your property. Furthermore, ACME will get rid of all rodents, which will stop any possibility of spreading a serious disease to you and your family members.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75a5794 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"75a5794\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>There are a number of ways rodents can spread diseases, including through bites, droppings and\/or body fluids. Mice do not only contaminate the food they eat; in fact, they can contaminate up to 10 times more food than they consume. Apart from the food that we eat, mice can also chew through a variety of indigestible materials and make severe damage to your house. With a mice control and rat control performed timely, rodents will not have a chance to harm your belongings.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-9a35143 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9a35143\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-6475a21\" data-id=\"6475a21\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef362e5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ef362e5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>You may try to keep the mice out of your house by using repellents available on the market. However, you can never be sure that you got rid of all the rodents because they usually live in dark void inside the infrastructure of your house. Installation in the attic, spaces between the floors and under bathtubs are some of the areas that rodents can populate. Only a professional mice exterminator\u00a0 and rat exterminator\u00a0 can reach these hidden places in your home by using professional tools and equipment for mice control and rat control.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c940bfd elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-global elementor-global-4670 elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"c940bfd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-lg\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/appointment\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Book An Appointment<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-d56e1c4\" data-id=\"d56e1c4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f9c9a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7f9c9a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"790\" height=\"527\" src=\"h